{"tid":1200453,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［山系行山撚］搵到個地方買行山野好多選擇","createTime":"2019-06-10T18:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T13:13:32.000Z","uid":177777,"like":350,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"aa513cca5b6f7ad8806a14f711b84d649b83097e","tid":1200453,"uid":177777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:02:06.000Z","msg":"我好鍾意行山<br />\n咁啱今日行開街 去到銅鑼灣間Decathlon <br />\n好似發現新大陸咁<br />\n重新改寫我對 行山嘅認知<br />\n原來我唔知道佢有咁多嘢賣 真係對行山好有用<br />\n想為大家介紹。<br />\n<br />\n頭先呢排成日突然間落雨<br />\n我唔知你有冇需要，但我對眼對沙石同樹葉好敏感<br />\n佢有多款泳鏡、有平有貴：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cjedg9f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCjedg9f.png&h=d686ec8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2YsBZnB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2YsBZnB.png&h=605b7b4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鍾意浮潛嘅朋友都有浮潛款：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UexqSHM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUexqSHM.png&h=004c412a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/na3tQur.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fna3tQur.png&h=93db5d30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vEp1q2N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvEp1q2N.png&h=72d9a588&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港有啲山剩係得石，好難爬，<br />\n如果需要更周全嘅保護，可能需要頭盔同護膝<br />\n我竟然又喺度搵到：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GfZs520.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGfZs520.png&h=181d90be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s6TNmBk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs6TNmBk.png&h=fb0e539c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遇上呢排嘅惡劣天氣，可能需要啲全身嘅雨衣，保護皮膚：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YwBOQuZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYwBOQuZ.png&h=d715b263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鍾意行山嘅朋友不妨分享俾多啲同路人睇<br />\n可能幫到下手<br />\n希望大家行山前做好準備"},{"pid":"68399a02b9bfa7fb702d1aa6a00de6334cad4247","tid":1200453,"uid":177777,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:02:36.000Z","msg":"可唔可以幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"628605dc7334f2f280accc7b64627f349263577d","tid":1200453,"uid":157522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:02:53.000Z","msg":"推推推推"},{"pid":"6cf12ce1f7422079a932af2d833ac6fe324b434c","tid":1200453,"uid":177777,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:03:20.000Z","msg":"唔係個個都知邊度有行山野賣"},{"pid":"f578a0501fa9040ad3461855667c2bc54f7b3a87","tid":1200453,"uid":218430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:03:55.000Z","msg":"推推推<br />\n好想行山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec4ede5db3660beab05581ee6348f0205b7217e","tid":1200453,"uid":33147,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:04:39.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝樓主介紹 終於可以瘋狂行山"},{"pid":"a46c850e8b4ba2f1522b7a40585d9acace6f3783","tid":1200453,"uid":124824,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:04:48.000Z","msg":"推 我決定聽日去行山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0923c1630e1bc9ad0d0c2c0387ec960da8b3c84","tid":1200453,"uid":177777,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:05:21.000Z","msg":"香港咁多靚嘅山<br />\n要行下架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba3cecaff9dee39ff6bfce9a2c3d09a970e598a","tid":1200453,"u